In the original song the love expresses by man is completely one sided. But now as a girl express her feelings it's clear she also love him. But the real brilliance comes when she says, and i quote
"Nazron Ne Teri Chhuwa, To Hai Yih Jaadu Hua, Hone Lagi Hoon Main Haseen"
Cause she knows, existence of HER beauty comes to life only because of  his pure love. 
Hats off to the composer's beautiful mind to add a female singer in this legendary song.
